rcase;color:#8a6a3f;margin:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">What each row tells you</p><div><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a18;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">The document, and the file</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#6f6e68;margin:3px 0 0;margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0">The title, plus the underlying file name and size — so you know what you are opening before you open it.</p></div><div><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:rgba(26,26,24,0.10);border-top-width:1px;margin:14px 0"/><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a18;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Fund and type</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#6f6e68;margin:3px 0 0;margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0">Which programme it belongs to, and whether it is legal, KYC / AML, financial, a report or a notice. Firm-wide papers show no fund.</p></div><div><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:rgba(26,26,24,0.10);border-top-width:1px;margin:14px 0"/><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a18;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Download</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#6f6e68;margin:3px 0 0;margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0">One action per row. The file opens in a new tab.</p></div></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="border-left:2px solid #b8915c;padding:2px 0 2px 14px;margin:0 0 22px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#6f6e68;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Download links are private and time-limited. They are generated for you when the page loads, which is why a copied link will not work later or for someone else — and why forwarding one does not share the document.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3a3a36;margin:0 0 14px;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-left:0">If the list grows long, press ⌘K — or Ctrl+K — anywhere in the portal to search your funds and documents, and to jump to any page.</p><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="text-align:center;margin:18px 0 4px"><tbody><tr><td><a href="{{{app_url}}}" style="line-height:100%;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;mso-padding-alt:0px;background-color:#1f3d2e;color:#ffffff;padding:12px 22px;border-radius:2px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;padding-top:12px;padding-right:22px;padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:22px" target="_blank"><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:366.66666666666663%;mso-text-raise:18" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;</i><![endif]--></span><span style="max-width:100%;display:inline-block;line-height:120%;mso-padding-alt:0px;mso-text-raise:9px">Open the data room</span><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:366.66666666666663%" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;&#8203;</i><![endif]--></span></a></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:rgba(26,26,24,0.10);margin:28px 0 14px"/><p style="font-size:10px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8a6a3f;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Day 6 of 7</p><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#6f6e68;margin:6px 0 0;margin-top:6px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0">Next: letters, and staying current.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:rgba(26,26,24,0.10);margin:0"/><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="padding:20px 32px;background-color:#1f3d2e"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:24px;font-family:&quot;JetBrains Mono&quot;, ui-monospace, Menlo, monospace;color:rgba(251,249,244,0.72);margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">{{{organization_name}}}</p><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:24px;font-family:&quot;JetBrains Mono&quot;, ui-monospace, Menlo, monospace;color:rgba(251,249,244,0.5);margin:0;margin-top:6px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">{{{organization_website}}} · <!-- -->Delivered by NewTaven</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><!--/$--></body></html>5:T56df,<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
