6:T500,{{{organization_name}}}

Documents · 6 of 7

Your documents.

{{{recipient_name}}} — reports, notices, statements and legal paperwork shared with you sit in one list, with the fund they belong to and the date they were filed.

What each row tells you

The document, and the file

The title, plus the underlying file name and size — so you know what you are opening before you open it.

----------------------------------------

Fund and type

Which programme it belongs to, and whether it is legal, KYC / AML, financial, a report or a notice. Firm-wide papers show no fund.

----------------------------------------

Download

One action per row. The file opens in a new tab.

Download links are private and time-limited. They are generated for you when the page loads, which is why a copied link will not work later or for someone else — and why forwarding one does not share the document.

If the list grows long, press ⌘K — or Ctrl+K — anywhere in the portal to search your funds and documents, and to jump to any page.

Open the data room {{{app_url}}}

